{"tid":390013,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同另一半無common friend既你地怕唔怕溝通有問題","createTime":"2017-09-06T17:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T06:26:31.000Z","uid":66719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8aa222fc71680bebc08d853046d6af399cf845d","tid":390013,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:28:46.000Z","msg":"拍左幾次拖,都同另一半無咩common friend<br />\n平時就無咩野既,不過鬧起交上黎,覺得好似欠左個橋樑去同佢修補關係咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋永遠只能夠同佢去D for兩個人既活動<br />\n大家都有各自圈子.不過互不相干,無一個有重疊<br />\n有時有D一大班人既活動,都想有佢既出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同佢一齊就好似世界得我同佢咁,咁樣其實正唔正常<br />\n<br />\n定好多人都同另一半無咩common friend"},{"pid":"02bb2e78b2343c2d8ac0311b47e8023fa3d40d99","tid":390013,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:33:22.000Z","msg":"同佢鬧交點解需要common friend 去做橋樑修補關係"},{"pid":"01290d2711e4742b6aa6d0cd66afd79433c475bc","tid":390013,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢鬧交點解需要common friend 去做橋樑修補關係</blockquote><br />\n我知呢個point無乜為,不過自己friend一定係幫自己既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想有個common friend可以持平D咁睇件事"},{"pid":"95704d1c534ca0ef4e52fe3ac6585f50f0248fbe","tid":390013,"uid":74262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:38:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ae939c4f2b61da126138c95b8ba7632549a7f2d","tid":390013,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係處女咪得 係處既話冇common fd都冇乜所謂</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67114e7264c48759085c3bc5d5a2d75a87a4e03b","tid":390013,"uid":13882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:46:13.000Z","msg":"同男朋友上網識，無共同朋友<br />\n唔覺得有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44b5452ea8dfe18792ed004dc77b6830da5daa5","tid":390013,"uid":66719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同男朋友上網識，無共同朋友<br />\n唔覺得有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有種佢隨時可以拍拍籮柚走左去既無力感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920079719498c0ade63afcf751f5c8cd3f87f302","tid":390013,"uid":13882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:10:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同男朋友上網識，無共同朋友<br />\n唔覺得有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有種佢隨時可以拍拍籮柚走左去既無力感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算有共同朋友佢都可以拍拍籮柚就走<br />\n你要做嘅野係令佢對你自己愈黎愈上心同<br />\n愈黎愈愛你"},{"pid":"7c64fc8ea33e720b6efa836a16ae0baa6a941678","tid":390013,"uid":140727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:26:30.000Z","msg":"係見佢啲朋友個陣好尷尬 <br />\n唔知講乜好"},{"pid":"0a7a358d43e74f3a6c4b123acfd49215ad423d1d","tid":390013,"uid":14217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:29:45.000Z","msg":"識埋佢d朋友"},{"pid":"f8f63b9230f76c32aefe507f92953cac761ab47c","tid":390013,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同男朋友上網識，無共同朋友<br />\n唔覺得有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有種佢隨時可以拍拍籮柚走左去既無力感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算有共同朋友佢都可以拍拍籮柚就走<br />\n你要做嘅野係令佢對你自己愈黎愈上心同<br />\n愈黎愈愛你</blockquote><br />\n都係既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係有種同佢少左種connection既機會咁"},{"pid":"42a7babe7e1a6c8f7be480dd0b0ac7f7ac0a299e","tid":390013,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係見佢啲朋友個陣好尷尬 <br />\n唔知講乜好</blockquote><br />\n咁每個朋友初相識都無咩共同話題<br />\n見多幾次先會無咁尷尬掛"},{"pid":"eb517b5992cec3e05f05ed429c0f07d7fc994de9","tid":390013,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識埋佢d朋友</blockquote><br />\n都要佢比機會我先得"}]}